text: Tasiman (died 7 December 2020) was an Indonesian politician. He was the Regent of the Pati Regency from 2001 to 2011. He was born in Juwana, Pati. Tasiman was chairman of the Regional People's Representative Assembly. Tasiman was a member of the Indonesian Democratic Party of Struggle. Tasiman died on 7 December 2020 from COVID-19 at a hospital in Medan, Indonesia.4 Hari Dirawat karena Positif Covid-19, Mantan Bupati Pati Tasiman Meninggal Dunia ==References== Category:2020 deaths Category:Indonesian politicians Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Indonesia
title: Tasiman
